org.eclipse.swt.events
Class TypedEvent

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.swt.events.TypedEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
ControlEvent, DisposeEvent, FocusEvent, KeyEvent, LocationEvent, MenuEvent, MobileDeviceEvent, ModifyEvent, MouseEvent, PaintEvent, ProgressEvent, ScreenEvent, SelectionEvent, ShellEvent, StatusTextEvent, TitleEvent
public class TypedEvent
extends java.lang.Object

This is the super class for all typed event classes provided by SWT. Typed events contain particular information which is applicable to the event occurance.

See Also:
